name: Dart Coinage
description:
Welcome to Dart Coinage! 

Inspired by the rant of  Conor McGergor's dad!

Use the Left & Right arrow keys to move! Remember you wear slim fit, hand fitted suit! Collect crisp 20 euro notes to keep your suit slim! Collecting coins will cause your suit to get big. It's Game Over if your suit gets too big!
